snippet.title: PROJECT ATHIA – Teaser Trailer | PS5 & PC
snippet.description:
Watch a breathtaking first look at PROJECT ATHIA (working title), a thrilling story-led, action-packed adventure from our new studio, Luminous Productions.

PROJECT ATHIA is the culmination of Luminous Productions’ philosophy to create a completely new and fresh gaming experiences that fuses together the latest technologies with art.

Coming to both PlayStation 5 and PC, with PROJECT ATHIA you can look forward to being transported to a vast and detailed world filled with beauty and dismay.

Learn more about #ProjectAthia, coming to PlayStation 5 & PC: https://sqex.link/projectathia 

Follow us for all the latest on PROJECT ATHIA
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SquareEnix
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/squareenix/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SquareEnix/
